OL,5, Convicted murderers and drug dealers   
OL,6, who have recently left prison in Russia
OL,7, face being conscripted to fight in     
OL,8, Ukraine under a change to the law.     
OL,10,FPresident Vladimir Putin amended the   
OL,11,Flegislation on calling up reservists to
OL,12,Finclude men convicted of serious crimes
OL,13,Fwho recently left prison.              
OL,15,FFormer prisoners convicted of sex      
OL,16,Fcrimes against children or terrorism   
OL,17,Fare still excluded from serving.       
OL,19,FRussian soldiers have been accused of  
OL,20,Fcrimes during the invasion of Ukraine. 
